":907963,"uid":25183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T12:29:10.000Z","msg":"用過佢黎交功課"},{"pid":"495ef1de912e37fb0e8a89b101d90346ac389972","tid":907963,"uid":3860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T12:32:08.000Z","msg":"以前有geocities 好多野睇<br />\n剩係有關lf2 都大把人整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd68c1fe00a66dfe9f0665651b8ea230543cbecb","tid":907963,"uid":8783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"495ef1de912e37fb0e8a89b101d90346ac389972","tid":907963,"uid":3860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T12:32:08.000Z","msg":"以前有geocities 好多野睇<br />\n剩係有關lf2 都大把人整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T12:35:02.000Z","msg":"Lf2 好多都係 個個咩MSN 社群到整<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我記得港版geocities 係得幾mb qouta<br />\n但日本版好似係無限，所以 有晒網上教學教你點申請日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7eeb30c39f54e6f9fda7630a1c5bfa1c837ea8f","tid":907963,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a75087d443c87c90f84cf909ae484168e8e09e08","tid":907963,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T12:19:43.000Z","msg":"果陣仲上bbs識筆友。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T12:46:59.000Z","msg":"ICQ溝女就有"}]}